data.description: Bring your offer!! Great Buy on the Golf Course!! Have the best of both worlds! Live in beautiful Brickshire located between Williamsburg and Richmond. One of the largest lots in the neighborhood on a premier golf course setting. Located on the 8th green and 9th tee and in the cul-de-sac! This lot is being offered below assessed value! You do not want to miss this opportunity! Seller is offering a free one year membership to Brickshire Golf Club with acceptable offer. Swimming, biking, walking trails, tennis, golfing, horseshoes, basketball and a gorgeous community building that residents can use as well as a workout center! Small stream on property. Sewer Connection fees already paid, over 10,000 value. Call Vicki Courrier to inquire about this lot 757 784 2165.  Awesome Location!!!
